OL,3,CNational Grid fined over #3m after
OL,4,Cpylon worker suffered life-changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FThe National Grid has been fined more
OL,8,Fthan #3m after a father-of-two was
OL,9,Fleft "lucky to be alive" with life-
OL,10,Fchanging injuries from working on a
OL,11,Fpylon in South Wales.
OL,13,FJustin Hollins was working replacing
OL,14,Fstep bolts on the pylon at Treforest
OL,15,FIndustrial Estate in Pontypridd on 3
OL,16,FDecember 2020, when he received an
OL,17,Felectric shock of 33 thousand volts.
