OL,3,CNational Grid fined over #3m after
OL,4,Cpylon worker suffered life-changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FThe 50-year-old sustained burns to 40%
OL,8,Fof his body, including to his arms and
OL,9,Flegs, and also lost part of his right
OL,10,Fbuttock.
OL,12,FNational Grid Electricity Distribution
OL,13,F(South Wales) Plc and 4 Power Ltd both
OL,14,Freceived fines in relation to the
OL,15,Fincident.
OL,17,FMr Hollins had to have six operations
OL,18,Fin the space of his first 10 days in
OL,19,Fhospital and required 24 hour care for
OL,20,Fmonths afterwards.
