OL,4,Cpylon worker suffered life-changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,F"This was a very difficult time, with
OL,8,Frelentless operations and endless,
OL,9,Fpainful changing of dressings", Mr
OL,10,FHollins said.
OL,12,F"Every day was a huge battle.
OL,14,F"I stopped needing to attend hospital
OL,15,Fappointments in August 2022 but will
OL,16,Fremain a burns patient for the rest of
OL,17,Fmy life.
