OL,7,F"At the time of my accident I was in
OL,8,Fpeak physical condition, which I was
OL,9,Ftold by the hospital is probably the
OL,10,Freason I survived.
OL,12,F"I have been stripped of the
OL,13,Fopportunity to provide for me family
OL,14,Fdoing the job I loved.
