OL,3,CNational Grid fined over #3m after
OL,4,Cpylon worker suffered life-changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,8,FSafety Executive (HSE) found that 4
OL,9,FPower Ltd who are based at Unit 1b,
OL,10,FIddenshall Hall Farm in Cheshire,
OL,11,Ffailed to properly plan and assess the
OL,12,Frisk.
OL,14,FHad this been done, it would have
OL,15,Fidentified that the arms of pylon were
OL,16,Ftoo short to do the work safely, while
OL,17,Fmaintaining the specified safety
OL,18,Fdistances as per industry standard.
