OL,3,CNational Grid fined over #3m after
OL,4,Cpylon worker suffered life-changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FNational Grid Electricity Distribution
OL,8,F(South Wales) Plc who are based at
OL,9,FAvonbank, Feeder Road, Bristol failed
OL,10,Fto ensure that the electricity was off
OL,11,Fin order to do this work safely on the
OL,12,Fpylon.
OL,14,F4 Power Ltd pleaded guilty to
OL,15,Fbreaching Section 2(1) of the Health
OL,16,Fand Safety at Work etc Act 1974 and
OL,17,Fhave been fined #80,000 and ordered to
OL,18,Fpay costs of #14,123.
