OL,7,FNational Grid Electricity Distribution
OL,8,F(South Wales) Plc pleaded guilty to
OL,9,Fbreaching Regulation 14 of the
OL,10,FElectricity at Work Regulations 1989
OL,11,Fand have been fined #3.2million and
OL,12,Fordered to pay costs of #20,460.
OL,14,FSpeaking after the hearing, HSE
OL,15,FInspector Rhys Hughes said: "The
OL,16,Finjuries sustained by Mr Hollins have
OL,17,Fbeen truly life-changing. He is lucky
OL,18,Fto be alive.
