OL,3,CNational Grid fined over #3m after
OL,4,Cpylon worker suffered life-changing
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,F"Those in control of work have a
OL,8,Fresponsibility to devise safe methods
OL,9,Fof working and to provide the
OL,10,Fnecessary information and instruction
OL,11,Fto workers.
OL,13,F"What is so frustrating in incidents
OL,14,Flike these is if a safe system of work
OL,15,Fhad been in place before the incident,
OL,16,Fhis injuries would have been prevented.
OL,18,F"HSE provides advice and guidance to
OL,19,Femployers and workers unsure of what
OL,20,Ftheir duties are or how to comply for
OL,21,Ffree on hse.gov.uk."
